posts.raw_content:
What conservatives keep failing to understand is that these are people who are seriously, and I mean seriously... Fucked up. Conservatives are healthy people. We think about our own self-interests. We are rational. Logical. We do what's good for us, and avoid what's bad for us... Simple enough.

Liberal women are not like that. Liberal women are sick human beings.

I want to make this clear... I am not an Andrew Tate style douchebag who thinks we should indulge or support anything that I am about to point out as the truth. I strongly believe that this behavior reflects a horrific, moral sickness that runs through liberal women. A moral sickness that no man should ever indulge. If you participate in liberal women's moral sickness. Then you are just as much a part of the problem as she is.

With that being said, I must point out that liberal women, at their core, are masochists. They want to be raped. They want to be brutalized. These are R-selected genetic mating strategies. They don't look out for their own self-interests the way a healthy minded person would. These are creatures who have sold their humanity and have been reduced to nothing more than a primal creature. They are indulging a deeply destructive primal instinct among women. The primal instinct of wanting to be conquered by powerful, dominant men. They are voting for and supporting all the things they do because they want to make it more likely to happen. If they bring in hordes of barbarians, release all the violent criminals, and defund the police. Then they literally hope that this will turn society into a free for all rape fest where the strongest men take turns killing each other and raping them as their reward.

As for us? The good men. The gentlemen. The ones who believe in chivalry? In protecting women? Who want nothing more than a sweet girl to love and protect?

They fucking hate us. They want us miserable, they want to make sure we never have a loyal girl. They don't even have enough mercy to line us up against the wall and put a bullet in our heads. They want us to be so miserable we wished we were dead.

The future of civilization, depends on our ability to suppress, target, and destroy this primal instinct among women. Past civilizations knew the survival of civilization depended on our ability to ruthlessly repress this instinct among women so deeply that women believed themselves to be the complete opposite of this. That women believed that they wanted a nice, gentle man. The masochistic instinct in women is what turns them into traitors. It makes them into sluts. It makes them selfish, narcissistic, and dare I say... Evil. Women's masochism must be repressed. Everything depends on it.

That is why I wish the right would focus on banning violent, extreme, and fetishy pornography. This is an absolutely critical issue that no one is talking about but we need to. We have to cut off the source of perversion in this nation or we are surely doomed.
